"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"But gas fees are likely to remain a huge issue in DeFi—no matter which chain you use.\\n\\nEthereum, the first and most popular smart contract-enabled layer-one blockchain, is extremely expensive to use. Simple token swaps on decentralized exchanges can cost hundreds of dollars, let alone more complex DeFi activity like [yield farming](https://decrypt.co/resources/what-is-yield-farming-beginners-guide).\\n\\nAnd this isn’t a particularly new phenomenon. If you remember back in 2017, a fun little crypto game [called](https://qz.com/1145833/cryptokitties-is-causing-ethereum-network-congestion/) CryptoKitties went viral and wreaked similar havoc on Ethereum’s gas fees.\",\"timestamp\":1638701437,\"title\":\"Ethereum has a gas fee problem\"},\"digest\":\"Ng25dp3YD3by7lw99NwZuW_loJ6B7D0TcX3RlXuR8j0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xB52bA587b8B27AC3F9b842dd2075aec1A150e1A7\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"onVo09QKnL4xeLRT3YHW9GfQ61odTW9KZvR5wginjlc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"biyO2ngdLTnAaaEJQ1uzmR1lV5hMTOQcoiuvjvnBfic\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"jgzFPuFqfPltjAopA1cTQ-9tkf0vUYFoPYzSRXb_sysXJVL9sSD-rf4sZqjsOT3550N-7_kyQNIQX8hi0w-RgQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x74f78148158d3f4dadaaeaa7dfa5a1c80469fae2638df18aced120705bf92ef6767db4deb08c278801bd28d567f32e4546ba9daf0627bf7813b27fe7015d02f51c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"onVo09QKnL4xeLRT3YHW9GfQ61odTW9KZvR5wginjlc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"biyO2ngdLTnAaaEJQ1uzmR1lV5hMTOQcoiuvjvnBfic\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Ng25dp3YD3by7lw99NwZuW_loJ6B7D0TcX3RlXuR8j0\"}"